Package: rsdk-image
Architecture: any
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, docker.io | docker-ce
Description: Offline Docker image package for Radxa SDK
 This package contains a pre-pulled Docker image tarball and will attempt
 to load it into Docker on installation if Docker is available on the host.
